descr: "A financial tool for tracking value accrued for a particular purpose.  In the healthcare field, used to track charges for a patient, cost centers, etc."

fields.name: coverage
fields.descr: "The party(s) that are responsible for payment (or part of) of charges applied to this account (including self-pay).\n\nA coverage may only be resposible for specific types of charges, and the sequence of the coverages in the account could be important when processing billing."

fields.name: priority
fields.descr: "The priority of the coverage in the context of this account."
